パソコン再起動の際に高確率（7/10）で、システム診断ライト点滅：橙2白7となり画面が真っ黒。

電源ボタン長押し15秒でシステム診断ライトが消え、再度電源ボタンで起動できる。
24H2をクリーンインストールした後に症状を確認。それまで使用していた社員が退職したので以前から発症していたのかは不明。

現在はWindows11 Pro 23H2をクリーンインストールし、症状は変わらず。
メモリやLCDケーブルの付け直し、Diagnostics異常なし。
translatedText:
When the computer is restarted, with a high probability (7/10), the system diagnostic light flashes: orange 2 white 7, and the screen is completely black.

The system diagnostic light turns off by pressing and holding the power button for 15 seconds, and you can start up again with the power button.
Check for symptoms after a clean install of 24H2. The employee who had used it until then has retired, so it is unclear whether the disease had developed before.

Currently, Windows 11 Pro 23H2 has been cleanly installed, and the symptoms have not changed.
The memory and LCD cable have been reattached, and there are no diagnostic problems.

5) Check all the boxes in the dialog box and select Delete my content.

3) Selecciona Eliminar un servicio de Google y, a continuación, haz clic en el icono de la papelera situado junto a YouTube.
4) Haz clic en Quiero eliminar mi cuenta de forma permanente.
5) Marca todas las casillas del cuadro de diálogo y selecciona Eliminar mi contenido.

Please follow the steps below:

2) Once the application is installed on the device, open the application and accept the Terms and Conditions.
3) On seeing the Call center window, Tap on Cancel and check if the application is asking for any 6-digit Connection code.

2) Una vez que la aplicación esté instalada en el dispositivo, ábrala y acepte los términos y condiciones.
3) Al ver la ventana del centro de llamadas, toque Cancelar y compruebe si la aplicación solicita algún código de conexión de 6 dígitos.

translatedText:
- Restart Laptop: Sometimes, simple problems can be solved by restarting.
- Connect External Mouse: Try using an external mouse to see if the problem is with the touchpad or the system as a whole.
- Check Connectors: Make sure all connectors (HDMI, USB, etc) are well connected and not loose.
Xs_Lenovo
